headline: JPMorgan Sets $324 PT on Public Storage (PSA), Maintains Overweight Rating
summary: Public Storage (NYSE:PSA) is one of the most undervalued stocks. On June 13, JPMorgan reiterated an Overweight rating on PSA, setting a price target of $324. The firm’s evaluation of Public Storage indicates confidence in its strategic market position and solid financial outcomes.
